// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2871 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 7a10c316-609e-54b0-87fa-36e329484bce

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
